<title type="html"><![CDATA[6/23 (Thu.) The School Shooting in Uvalde, Texas, US /Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's Lawsuit (Host: Michael)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=628&amp;p=651#p651"><![CDATA[
Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session 1 : What to know about the school shooting in Uvalde, Texas, US<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.nytimes.com/article/uvalde-texas-school-shooting.html">https://www.nytimes.com/article/uvalde- ... oting.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Why does the US have so many mass shootings?<br />2.Why can't America do anything to stop mass shootings?<br />3.Do you agree with the 2nd Amendment of the United States Constitution:&quot;The right of the people to keep and bear Arms shall not be infringed.&quot;?  <br />4.Is mental health the reason for the excessive mass shootings in the US?<br />5.What will the scenario be if Taiwanese can buy guns freely?<br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session 2: Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's Lawsuit<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2022/06/01/entertainment/johnny-depp-amber-heard-verdict/index.html">https://edition.cnn.com/2022/06/01/ente ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.In court Johnny Depp won the lawsuit, but do you think who really won the lawsuit?<br />2.Do you think women also abuse men sometimes?<br />3.Do you think social media played any role in the trial?<br />4.If you had watched the trial, what do you think of the performance of Johnny Depp's lawyer-Camille Vasquez?<br />5.Do you think their acting careers can still recover?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=25437">Michael</a> — Fri Jun 17, 2022 3:28 pm</p><hr />
